-william-h-macy-17-sundays-hulu.png?resize=1200,816 1200w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/chris-meloni-william-h-macy-17-sundays-hulu.png?resize=41,28 41w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/chris-meloni-william-h-macy-17-sundays-hulu.png?resize=247,168 247w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/chris-meloni-william-h-macy-17-sundays-hulu.png?resize=496,337 496w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/chris-meloni-william-h-macy-17-sundays-hulu.png?resize=993,675 993w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/chris-meloni-william-h-macy-17-sundays-hulu.png?resize=294,200 294w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/chris-meloni-william-h-macy-17-sundays-hulu.png?resize=588,400 588w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/chris-meloni-william-h-macy-17-sundays-hulu.png?resize=1177,800 1177w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/chris-meloni-william-h-macy-17-sundays-hulu.png?resize=37,25 37w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/chris-meloni-william-h-macy-17-sundays-hulu.png?resize=221,150 221w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/chris-meloni-william-h-macy-17-sundays-hulu.png?resize=883,600 883w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/chris-meloni-william-h-macy-17-sundays-hulu.png?resize=150,102 150w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/chris-meloni-william-h-macy-17-sundays-hulu.png?resize=110,75 110w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/chris-meloni-william-h-macy-17-sundays-hulu.png?resize=285,194 285w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/chris-meloni-william-h-macy-17-sundays-hulu.png?resize=320,218 320w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/chris-meloni-william-h-macy-17-sundays-hulu.png?resize=640,435 640w, https://tvline.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/chris-meloni-william-h-macy-17-sundays-hulu.png?resize=800,544 800w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eMeloni is best known for playing Det. Elliot Stabler, a role he originated on \u003cem\u003eLaw \u0026amp; Order: SVU \u003c/em\u003eand now plays on Peacock’s \u003cem\u003eLaw \u0026amp; Order: Organized Crime\u003c/em\u003e. His other TV credits include \u003cem\u003eOz\u003c/em\u003e, \u003cem\u003eHappy!\u003c/em\u003e and \u003cem\u003eUnderground\u003c/em\u003e. Macy was a six-time Emmy nominee for his role as patriarch Frank Gallagher on Showtime’s \u003cem\u003eShameless\u003c/em\u003e and previously recurred on \u003cem\u003eER\u003c/em\u003e; he’s mainly known for his film works in movies like \u003cem\u003eFargo\u003c/em\u003e, \u003cem\u003eBoogie Nights\u003c/em\u003e and \u003cem\u003eMagnolia\u003c/em\u003e. \u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eFor all you \u003cem\u003eLaw \u0026amp; Order: OC\u003c/em\u003e fans worried about this news, Meloni’s casting here does not necessarily spell doom for \u003cem\u003eOC\u003c/em\u003e, a source maintains, and here’s why: \u003cem\u003e17 Sundays\u003c/em\u003e would shoot in the fall, while \u003cem\u003eOrganized Crime\u003c/em\u003e — if it’s renewed for Season 6 — would return to production in the spring. Season 5 of \u003cem\u003eOrganized Crime\u003c/em\u003e wrapped up its 10-episode run in June. \u003cem\u003e(Additional reporting by Kimberly Roots and Michael Ausiello)\u003c/em\u003e\n\n\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eAre you ready to hit the field with Hulu, now that Meloni and Macy are warming up? Join us in the comments to share your thoughts on the casting news.\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
